{"tid":2112734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"RTHK 31-- <<想點>>：法治其實係乜？","createTime":"2020-07-17T14:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T00:13:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d2853fd1b55cf18e45b2cbef0359155d5fa6dbf8","tid":2112734,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T14:10:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fRfmGpHJIDI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfRfmGpHJIDI&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=251b1c89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fRfmGpHJIDI</a><br />\n<br />\n法治是香港的核心價值，是香港成功的基石。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;但，法治其實是甚麼？<br />\n如何區分法治（rule of law）與以法管治（rule by law）和人治（rule of man）？<br />\n甚麼行為會破壞法治？誰才有能力破壞法治？<br />\n<br />\n【講你想點】<br />\n守法就是法治？執法不公對法治有何影響？普世的法治與中國式法治，香港選哪套？港區國安法生效，香港法治健康狀況如何？<br />\n<br />\n嘉賓：<br />\n陳景生（資深大律師、大律師公會前主席、法律界選委）<br />\n何家祈Alan（政府助學金聯合委員會委員、監警會觀察員）<br />\n鄒晁琳Leo（中文大學政治與行政學系二年級）<br />\n戴穎姿Angie（法律系三年級、Sound of the Silenced 召集人、義務律師團後勤支援）<br />\n顏雋Lucas（青年發展委員會成員、中學教師、青賢智匯成員、創辦初創企業）<br />\n<br />\n【社會實驗】一場有規則可依、裁判依法執法的比賽，如何違反法治精神？<br />\n【想問】法治精神的元素在香港還好嗎？<br />\n【即係點】包青天公正嚴明，原來破壞法治？<br />\n<br />\n主持：麥嘉緯"},{"pid":"9a654c95d2700ec5a99dca76657bdc54c71ed8f8","tid":2112734,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d383ddab9312ca0766c738276f0beb1e442960","tid":2112734,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T14:10:54.000Z","msg":"有興趣<img src